WEBVTT


00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:03.559
despite being nearly isolated in the world stage,

00:00:03.560 --> 00:00:06.420
Russia still has more allies than you might think.

00:00:06.720 --> 00:00:09.100
Belarus is the biggest supporter of Russia,

00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:09.919
allowing putin's

00:00:09.920 --> 00:00:12.380
forces to freely move through its territory.

00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:13.839
in the Middle East,

00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:16.479
Iran remains one of moscow's most reliable

00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:17.679
regional partners.

00:00:17.680 --> 00:00:20.319
in fact, the regime recently agreed to help Russia

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:22.900
manufacture war drones to fight Ukraine.

00:00:23.080 --> 00:00:26.439
putin's Russia also has the unwavering support of Syria,

00:00:26.440 --> 00:00:28.399
with Assad sending troops to fight

00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:29.679
alongside Russian forces

00:00:29.680 --> 00:00:31.879
last spring. in Asia,

00:00:31.880 --> 00:00:35.180
Moscow managed to forge closer ties with North Korea.

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:37.759
some reports suggest that the Hermit Kingdom has been

00:00:37.760 --> 00:00:39.279
shipping munitions to Russia,

00:00:39.280 --> 00:00:41.279
although Pyongyang has repeatedly denied

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:42.460
these allegations.

00:00:42.640 --> 00:00:44.479
across the Pacific, Cuba

00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:47.540
continues to be one of putin's loudest cheerleaders,

00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:50.780
fully adopting the Kremlins narrative about Ukraine.

00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:53.159
the same can be said of Venezuela,

00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:53.879
the key Geo

00:00:53.880 --> 00:00:55.359
strategic ally of Russia,

00:00:55.360 --> 00:00:58.500
who was one of the first to publicly back putin's war.

00:00:58.920 --> 00:01:02.239
finally, Russia has expanded its tactical cooperation

00:01:02.240 --> 00:01:03.239
with Nicaragua,

00:01:03.240 --> 00:01:04.799
a nation that gave Moscow

00:01:04.800 --> 00:01:06.639
full authority to deploy military

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:09.140
assets on its territory as of June.
